    Grab a pair of shoes, tuck the suit buttons, its wedding time. If you want to tell stories about the fun you had at your wedding, Sachin Studios is the place for you. Covering the smiles, the love, the tears, the excitement is what we do at weddings. Sachin Studios is a wedding photography firm established in August 2014 by two engineers.

     

    The vision of Sachin Studios is to create eternal memories for the end users while covering the commotion, ebullience and joviality of their weddings.

    Happily Ever Afterwords

    We chose Sachin Studios based on glowing recommendations from friends, and they exceeded our expectations in every way. From our initial consultation to the final delivery, their team was the epitome of professionalism and warmth. Their standout offering—the fully edited traditional video coverage—allowed us and our families to relive each cherished moment of our wedding day with vivid clarity and emotion. ￼

    On the ground, the Sachin Studios team was a delight to work with—accommodating, unobtrusive, and genuinely in tune with the atmosphere of our events. They seamlessly captured every significant moment without disrupting the natural flow, truly understanding the essence of our celebrations.

    Their post-production services were equally impressive, demonstrating a keen willingness to incorporate our feedback and make necessary adjustments to ensure our complete satisfaction.

    In summary, Sachin Studios provided an exceptional experience, blending technical expertise with heartfelt storytelling. We wholeheartedly recommend them to anyone seeking to immortalize their special day through stunning photography and videography

    ​

    ~ Akshita & Shivam
